  "name": "\"Коли питатимуть за мною...\"",
  "link": "/metrs_poem.php?poem=8200",
  "html": "\n<h4></h4>\n\n<a href=\"/metrs.php?id=327&amp;type=tvorch\" class=\"redhr1\">Творчість</a> |\n<a href=\"/metrs.php?id=327&amp;type=biogr\" class=\"redhr1\">Біографія</a> |\n<a href=\"/metrs.php?id=327&amp;type=critiques\" class=\"redhr1\">Критика</a>\n\n<h4>\"Коли питатимуть за мною...\"</h4>\n<!--<div style=\"float:right;margin-left: 10px\">\n\t<script async src=\"//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js\"></script>\n\n\t<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\n\t\t style=\"display:inline-block;width:250px;height:400px\"\n\t\t data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5357335372099528\"\n\t\t data-ad-slot=\"7581761695\"></ins>\n\t<script>\n\t(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n\t</script>\n</div>-->\n\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Якщо &nbsp;питатимуть &nbsp;за &nbsp;мною,<br>\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;то &nbsp;скажи: &nbsp;у &nbsp;нього &nbsp;була &nbsp;справа<br>\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;в &nbsp;потойбіччі.<br>\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Сокан<br>\n<br>\nКоли &nbsp;питатимуть &nbsp;за &nbsp;мною,<br>\nто &nbsp;скажіть,<br>\nщо &nbsp;води &nbsp;обмивають &nbsp;камінь<br>\nі &nbsp;пливуть,<br>\nщо &nbsp;вітер &nbsp;гусне<br>\nв &nbsp;нерухомій &nbsp;тишині,<br>\nщо &nbsp;лірика &nbsp;долонь<br>\nв &nbsp;жіночому &nbsp;волоссі<br>\nзмивається &nbsp;часом.<br>\n<br>\nЯкщо &nbsp;питатимуть &nbsp;за &nbsp;мною,<br>\nто &nbsp;скажіть.<br>\n<br>\n\n\n\n<br><br>\n"
}